#### How to use

Check the [Read Me](https://github.com/nadundesilva/mesh-manager/tree/{{VERSION_TAG}}#how-to-use) for instructions on how to use the Operator.

#### Changelog:

- Upgrade to Operator Framework v1.27.0
- Fix vulnerabilities
  - CVE-2022-41717
  - CVE-2022-41721
- Add support for multiple CPU architectures in Controller workloads
  - amd64
  - arm64
  - ppc64le
  - s390x
- Add default runtime profile to Controller deployment
